import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Home, Login, Register } from '../../pages'


const Routers = () => {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Route>
        <Routes path='/login'>
          <Login />
        </Routes>
        <Routes path='/register'>
          <Register />
        </Routes>
        <Routes path='/'>
          <Home />
        </Routes>
      </Route>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default Router
